>\n\n::: {#table11}\n:::\n\n::: terra-table-title\nTable 11. Herpetofauna Species Dataset\n:::\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-5ccd2c7b44692b07c717\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-5ccd2c7b44692b07c717\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"data\":[[\"Proyecto ACAC\",null,\"# Transecto\",\"1\",\"1\",\"2\",\"3\",\"3\",\"4\",\"4\",\"5\",\"5\",\"6\"],[\"Francisco J. Mujica\",null,\"Coord. Inicio\",\"216798, 2131610, 16Q\",\"216798, 2131610, 16Q\",\"216429, 2132265, 16Q\",\"215526, 2132423, 16Q\",\"215526, 2132423, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"215526, 2132423, 16Q\",\"215526, 2132423, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\"],[null,null,\"Coord. Final\",\"216429, 2132265, 16Q\",\"216429, 2132265, 16Q\",\"216026, 2132918, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"216501, 2131641, 16Q\",\"216501, 2131641, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"215539, 2131768, 16Q\",\"216501, 2131641, 16Q\"],[\"Pedro Nahuat\",null,\"Fecha\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45056\",\"45057\",\"45057\",\"45057\"],[null,null,\"Hora\",\"0.76874999999999993\",\"0.76874999999999993\",\"0.80555555555555547\",\"0.84027777777777779\",\"0.84027777777777779\",\"0.87152777777777779\",\"0.87152777777777779\",\"0.29166666666666669\",\"0.29166666666666669\",\"0.32291666666666669\"],[null,null,\"Nombre común\",\"Lagartija espinosa de puntos amarillos\",\"Abaniquillo liso del sureste\",\"Abaniquillo yucateco\",\"Basilisco café\",\"Abaniquillo liso del sureste\",\"Iguana de cola espinosa yucateca\",\"Rana arborícola lechosa\",\"Ameiva arcoíris\",\"Lagartija espinosa de puntos amarillos\",\"Lagartija espinosa de puntos amarillos\"],[null,null,\"Nombre científico\",\"Sceloporus chrysostictus\",\"Norops rodriguezii\",\"Norops ustus\",\"Basiliscus vittatus\",\"Norops rodriguezii\"